FEMALE (
paratype
): Total length 4.7, carapace width 1.3, tibia 2: 5.6, tibia 4: 5.3 (others missing). In general very similar to male, but femora without spines, and dark stripes on opisthosoma more distinct. Epigynum simple plate (fig. 901).
